Music::NeoRiemannianTonnetz - performs Neo-Riemann operations on triads

To install this module, use CPAN, for example:

  cpanm Music::NeoRiemannianTonnetz

For the current release, see:

http://github.com/thrig/Music-NeoRiemannianTonnetz

which can be installed by cloning that directory then running `cpanm .`
therein.

DEPENDENCIES

Some knowledge of music theory will likely benefit the user, for this
module, in particular:

https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Neo-Riemannian_theory

